      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『もし恋』の発売日前日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ",
      "startTime": 2.4666667064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "どうした？　元気がないみたいだが……\nもしかして体調でも悪いのか？",
      "startTime": 8.0772192299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.926326255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、体調は大丈夫だよ\nでも、もし恋のことが気になっちゃって……",
      "startTime": 14.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.7475509126
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "収録は頑張ったけど、どんな風に出来上がったのかな\nって不安で……何をしててもずっと考えちゃうの",
      "startTime": 22.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんや渚ちゃんみたいに出来なかったら……\nみんなをドキドキさせられなかったらどうしよう……",
      "startTime": 31.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.1631291509
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちは分かるが、まずはプレイしてみないとな\nサンプルが届いているから、今から一緒にやってみよう",
      "startTime": 39.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん。まずはやってみないとだよね\n{user}さんと一緒なら出来る気がする！",
      "startTime": 47.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "始まった……うぅ……ドキドキするよ……\nあれ、このドキドキってもしかして恋！？",
      "startTime": 59.9999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "違うだろ。それは緊張のドキドキだ\nほら、ストーリーを進めるぞ",
      "startTime": 70.5666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.121721502
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるよ～。あ、ここの遊びに誘う時の演技凄く\n自信があるんだよ！　収録でも一回でOKだったの！",
      "startTime": 79.4999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.5435304045
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "ねえねえ、やっぱり芽衣、転び過ぎじゃない？\n確かに川は滑りやすいけど……でも、いいシーンだね",
      "startTime": 90.4999933879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.5009897034
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（あんなに不安そうだったのに）\n（すっかりゲームに夢中になっているな）",
      "startTime": 98.6999933879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣もしっかり楽しんでくれて良かったよ\nこれならファンも喜んでくれそうだな",
      "startTime": 104.5666600545,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.2761822502
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "うん、喜んでくれるといいな～\nあ、もしかしてこの次のシーンって……",
      "startTime": 110.6510681138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり！　{user}さんとの雨宿りを\n思い出しながら、いーっぱいアンケートに書いたんだよ",
      "startTime": 119.9999933879,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、恋愛はよく分からないけど\n好きな人との雨宿りは楽しいだろうな～って思って",
      "startTime": 128.0333236694,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣の楽しい気持ちをみんなにも知ってほしくて\nだからゲームにも入れてほしかったんだよね",
      "startTime": 136.6085538075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに再現してくれるなんて凄いなぁ\nあ、あれ……？　でも、こんなにくっついてたっけ？",
      "startTime": 144.5601780511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛ゲームだからな\nプレイヤーが喜ぶ描写に寄せたんだろう",
      "startTime": 152.5666570026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.5903734723
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ……そっか……あ、あれれ、どうしよう\nなんだか不思議な気分になってきちゃった",
      "startTime": 165.1622634119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.908739372
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "胸がもやもやしてるけどあったかくて……\n怜ちゃん達のもし恋をプレイした時みたいな……",
      "startTime": 173.9999893187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.119986085
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "……あの時、{user}さんと雨宿りしてた\n芽衣も、ゲームの中の芽衣と同じ気持ちだったのかな",
      "startTime": 181.033322652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、さすがに同じじゃないはず……\nでも、シチュエーションは同じだし……",
      "startTime": 192.0333318073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 195.8710383056
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "えー？　どうしよう、分かんないよ\n{user}さんどう思う！？",
      "startTime": 198.9666651407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――もし恋発売後　イベント会場にて",
      "startTime": 201.8615149138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.6081959364
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.694871644
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "見て見て～！　プロモーション用に\nゲームの中の芽衣とお揃いの衣装を作ってもらったの！",
      "startTime": 207.4333318073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "よく似合ってるよ。毎回思うが、もし恋のプロモは\n衣装までこだわっているよな",
      "startTime": 215.6666651407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 217.8518102602
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "本当に凄いよね！　ファンのみんなも、「ゲームの\n中と一緒だ！」ってびっくりしてくれるといいな",
      "startTime": 221.4333318073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 225.1880231814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei021.m4a",
      "text": "さっき会場の様子をちょっとだけ見て来たんだけど\n満員だったよ！",
      "startTime": 228.3333318073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 230.2457559542
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_03-mei022.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣のもし恋のために\nこんなに沢山の人達が集まってくれるなんて嬉しいな～",
      "startTime": 232.0666651407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 237.2937151865
